AT the Sessions of Peace , Oyer and Terminer , and Goal Delivery of Newgate ; Held at Justice-Hall in the Old-Bayly , on Wednesday

October , 1687 . Before the Right Honourable Sir John Peak , Kt . Lord Mayor of the City of London , with others of His Majesties Justices of the Peace for London and Middlesex . The Jurors were , viz . London Jury .
